BT 1 0 0 1 0 111 Tm /F1 9 Tf 12 TL (The Wike Coherence Law C = C_0 x exp\(-alphagamma_eff\) has been applied across biology \(Papers 01-88\), quantum) Tj T* (hardware \(Papers 14, 65, 76, 77, 81\), ecology \(Paper 83\), finance \(Paper 88\), and sociology \(Paper 86\). This paper derives) Tj T* (it from first principles using the Lindblad master equation -- the standard formalism for open quantum systems. The) Tj T* (derivation establishes: \(1\) the Wike Coherence Law follows exactly from Born-Markov-secular Lindblad dynamics; \(2\)) Tj T* (gamma_c is a real critical point defined by the balance between Bootstrap entropy suppression and environmental) Tj T* (decoherence; \(3\) the same critical structure appears in superconductivity \(BCS T_c\), the Berezinskii-Kosterlitz-Thouless) Tj T* (\(BKT\) transition, the laser threshold, Frohlich condensation, and Bose-Einstein condensation -- all are the same gamma_c) Tj T* (condition in different physical languages; \(4\) the Wike exponent alpha_W = 1 + 1/nu\(3D Ising\) = 2.587 is now formally) Tj T* (named, with nu = 0.6298 from conformal bootstrap to 0.1% \(Paper 84\). The framework is not an analogy. It is a phase) Tj T* (transition, and all phase transitions are instances of it.) Tj T* ET
